  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Visual Pathfinder (LACE inc.) offers a non- invasive, patient- centered visual
      rehabilitation system based on an acoustic biofeedback. The investigators wanted to evaluate
      its usefulness in the improvement of visual function in visually impaired patients with high
      myopia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
